Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.75,0:00:07.10,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,這場戀愛令人戰慄，震驚，焦慮難耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.35,0:00:10.70,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,受不可名狀的力量驅使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.80,0:00:18.30,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,來勢洶湧讓人無法禁閉心扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.30,0:00:36.25,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,我們感受得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.80,0:00:46.90,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,愛情的利刺或許同樣加之於你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.00,0:00:53.40,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,不知你究竟為何心痛 為何膽怯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.55,0:00:58.00,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕去面對糾葛不清的二人真實面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.10,0:01:01.50,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,生怕面對彼此的事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.35,0:01:06.90,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,這場戀愛令人戰慄，震驚，焦慮難耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.00,0:01:14.15,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,即使迷茫想時似乎隨著清風而逝 仍然無法抱個滿懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.25,0:01:17.60,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在我小小的胸臆中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.75,0:01:21.22,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,無法緊閉心扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.32,0:01:25.75,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,深藏著朝著下一步邁進的惶惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.80,0:01:35.20,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,500)}即使我已將迷惑擁個滿懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.70,0:22:36.90,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,透過窗戶看到天空 描繪著飛機留下的雲跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.90,0:22:45.30,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,淨是回想今天和你爭吵的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.80,0:22:55.95,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,瑣碎的事情弄得束手無策 坐立不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.95,0:23:00.50,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,不自然地馬上給你打電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.60,0:23:04.10,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,還是喜歡看到你迷人的笑臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.50,0:23:09.45,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,非常幸福的時光將要來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.55,0:23:14.60,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,伴隨著痛苦的腳步聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.70,0:23:23.45,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,過於多心反而陷入更深的困境 然而卻又守侯在你的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.50,0:23:32.40,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,夏之幻想 合上雙眼最先浮現眼前的還是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.90,0:23:36.70,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,別無所求 只想和你在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.80,0:23:41.95,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,就算束手無策也願意 緊牽的手永不放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.80,0:00:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,堅強的內心蘊含著推理的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.50,0:00:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠以最強勁的節奏揭開事件的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.50,0:00:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看上去總是很嚴肅的員警們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.80,0:00:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也會為了事件與愛情而奮鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.90,0:00:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.50,0:00:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 頭腦卻是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.30,0:00:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.10,0:02:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來…乖小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.80,0:02:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長大 不停地長大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.50,0:02:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,燒得更猛烈一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.00,0:02:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把所有的罪惡燃燒起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.10,0:02:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還需要一根火柴 還要一根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.20,0:02:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能結束一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.70,0:02:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨後這紅色的火焰便會燒掉整個東京
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.80,0:03:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使一切重新開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.20,0:03:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.70,0:03:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.90,0:03:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.90,0:03:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走 回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.10,0:03:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.80,0:03:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本廳的刑事戀愛物語3 (前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.30,0:03:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警視廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.10,0:03:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.40,0:03:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人的眼睛長什麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.10,0:03:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.40,0:03:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛像狐狸一樣往上吊 就這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.10,0:03:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛往上吊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.40,0:03:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是像這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.80,0:04:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.30,0:04:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.00,0:04:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳畫得好難看哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.10,0:04:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全像是小孩子在塗鴉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.80,0:04:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有其他畫的比較好的人了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.30,0:04:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畫師的媽媽今天感冒 他請了假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.20,0:04:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.50,0:04:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確是呢 佐藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.80,0:04:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.10,0:04:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種畫怎麼也無法交給搜查人員啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.10,0:04:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然線條俐落 畫風耐人尋味 但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.30,0:04:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.60,0:04:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你們來畫得可愛點讓我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.50,0:04:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩位先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.60,0:04:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個 畫畫嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我擅長的是印象畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.40,0:04:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等…白鳥 差勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.40,0:04:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 這個人其實也未必是縱火犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.50,0:04:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 你是說步美在說謊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.80,0:05:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別把小孩子當傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.00,0:05:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是她又沒有親眼看到那個男人縱火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.00,0:05:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.10,0:05:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天氣這麼熱 那個人還穿著長大衣 帶著手套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.00,0:05:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,褲子上還有被汽油潑到的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.70,0:05:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還帶著詭異的笑容出現在縱火現場的街道中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.10,0:05:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的人如果不是縱火犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.10,0:05:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是太說不過去了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.00,0:05:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.00,0:05:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的吧 步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.20,0:05:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.10,0:05:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.10,0:05:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之 大家一起去犯罪現場看看怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.70,0:05:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也去（太好了）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.80,0:05:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我開車送你們去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.50,0:05:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必了 我要順道繞到別的地方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.70,0:05:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為剛好順路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.50,0:05:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到別處去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.80,0:05:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天對我而言是一個特別的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特…特別的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.60,0:06:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤的生日嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.20,0:06:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正好相反
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.00,0:06:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相反
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.70,0:06:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底要去哪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.20,0:06:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.80,0:06:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我想起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.00,0:06:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是佐藤父親佐藤正義警官的忌日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.20,0:06:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是他的殉職日了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.70,0:06:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.30,0:06:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.80,0:06:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.10,0:06:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正好是十八年前的今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.30,0:06:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在追捕銀行搶匪途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.20,0:06:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這個咖啡店這裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.50,0:06:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這咖啡店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.40,0:07:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.60,0:07:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這個咖啡店門口被大卡車撞倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.90,0:07:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不幸的是天下著大雨 救護車來得太遲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.80,0:07:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤警官是躺在救護車上在家人的陪伴下斷氣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警部那裡聽來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.10,0:07:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那件案子的名字好像是叫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.70,0:07:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愁思郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.70,0:07:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 愁思郎 就是愁思郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.60,0:07:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於被卡車撞倒的警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.90,0:07:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷地對逃走的犯人叫著這個謎樣的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.80,0:07:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才被命名為愁思郎事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.20,0:07:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時員警還展開了大規模的搜查網
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.80,0:07:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是因為掌握核心事件的警官已經過世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.80,0:07:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以偵查行動便停頓下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.60,0:07:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三年前這件事已經過了追訴時效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.70,0:07:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事我是聽小五郎叔叔說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.70,0:08:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個事件我知道 在電視上看到過好幾次呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.70,0:08:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.70,0:08:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是一項計畫周密的犯罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.40,0:08:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的線索只有銀行監視器拍攝下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.10,0:08:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不到十秒鐘的畫面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.80,0:08:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不知道已經殉職的警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.10,0:08:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是根據何種方法鎖定嫌疑犯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.50,0:08:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個事件就在重重迷霧中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.00,0:08:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但萬萬沒想到那位警官竟然就是佐藤的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.30,0:08:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.40,0:08:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人們往往只記住案犯姓名和犯罪經過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.70,0:08:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰又會記得案件中殉職的員警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.10,0:08:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非是員警或者別的有關人士才會記住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.30,0:08:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐…佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.20,0:08:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們工作並不是為了讓大家記住我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.20,0:08:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可當時那個卡車司機沒有看到犯人的臉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.10,0:09:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 犯人好像當時穿著長長的雨披
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.40,0:09:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此是男是女都分辨不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.10,0:09:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且銀行監視器拍到的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.50,0:09:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴著帽子 太陽眼鏡和口罩 穿著大衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.80,0:09:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是已經知道犯人的名字叫“愁思郎”了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.50,0:09:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒有任何一個叫這個名字的人有涉案的嫌疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.40,0:09:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難怪整個案件就像是在重重迷霧中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.70,0:09:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,線索只有監視器拍到的畫面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.40,0:09:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿著雨衣的犯人身影和“愁思郎”這三個字而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.70,0:09:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有四條線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.40,0:09:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第四條線索是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.20,0:09:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父親寫在員警手冊上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.30,0:09:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三個奇怪的片假名 カンオ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.10,0:09:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,カンオ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.80,0:09:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是第一次聽到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.30,0:09:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警方似乎沒透露這件事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.60,0:09:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為其他員警都沒聽父親說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.80,0:09:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但從父親前後的記述來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.10,0:09:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有密切的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.50,0:09:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且當時我記得我跟我媽還被問了好幾次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.10,0:10:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然…然後呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.70,0:10:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一次都沒聽說過 而且根本不明白其涵義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.20,0:10:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我小時候曾盯著這三個字很用心地想過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.50,0:10:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果誰能幫我解開這個謎 把愁思郎給逮捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.30,0:10:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我願意為他做任何事 達成他的所有願望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.30,0:10:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 任何…要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.70,0:10:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要一千份鰻魚飯可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.90,0:10:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.10,0:10:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去多羅碧加樂園看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.20,0:10:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要國際宇宙車站的車票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.50,0:10:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我呢 會要個PRADA的名牌皮包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.30,0:10:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以要這屆世界盃足球賽的入場券嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.00,0:10:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這幫小孩子真是現實得恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.70,0:10:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 你們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.10,0:10:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你們看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.80,0:11:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.80,0:11:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是美和子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.00,0:11:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳長大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.20,0:11:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們認識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.50,0:11:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是爸爸高中時代的棒球隊的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.70,0:11:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我爸爸的最佳拍檔 投手猿渡秀朗先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.50,0:11:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.30,0:11:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以臂力強腳程快著稱的鹿野修二先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.90,0:11:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.50,0:11:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,值得信賴的第四棒豬保滿雄先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.30,0:11:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有美麗的球隊經理神鳥蝶子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.50,0:11:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別笑話我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.70,0:11:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都已經是五十歲的老太婆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.60,0:11:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天大家怎麼都在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.90,0:11:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家好久沒見 想聚聚喝上一杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.20,0:11:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前跟佐藤隊長打個招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.00,0:11:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天一起來看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.60,0:11:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.00,0:11:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果以前沒有邀請他 他都會生氣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.10,0:12:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（我們還是在那家居酒屋）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.30,0:12:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我是白鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.20,0:12:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（妳工作結束後也來坐坐吧）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.00,0:12:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 目暮警部 現在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.40,0:12:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在在杯戶町第四條街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.60,0:12:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人發現像縱火犯的可疑人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.90,0:12:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 地點就走品川的第六條街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.20,0:12:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有個男人在臨檢的時候突然逃跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.30,0:12:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前正在追捕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.80,0:12:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的特徵是長髮 戴帽子 穿著灰色的長大衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.70,0:12:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,位置離你們很近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子就托佐藤看著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.60,0:12:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和高木立刻趕往現場支援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.30,0:12:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情就這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.80,0:12:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.30,0:12:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.50,0:12:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 快上車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.70,0:12:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,員警證…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.20,0:12:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手槍…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.00,0:12:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.90,0:12:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.70,0:13:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手銬 手銬放在一科的桌子上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.10,0:13:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間回去拿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.30,0:13:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係吧 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.60,0:13:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.90,0:13:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一有狀況 還有白鳥警官的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.80,0:13:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我看過雜誌上的占星專欄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.80,0:13:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天可是超級幸運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.80,0:13:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有帶手銬也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.20,0:13:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正只是一個縱火犯而已嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.40,0:13:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公 小心些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.70,0:13:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.10,0:13:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,占卜的說我今天會很順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.40,0:13:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 爸爸忘了帶手銬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.60,0:13:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我先生 被車撞倒了 現在在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.60,0:13:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.60,0:13:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸明明是站在正義一方的 你為正義而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.20,0:13:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.10,0:14:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 所謂正義就是…就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.50,0:14:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤 佐藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.40,0:14:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.00,0:14:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.60,0:14:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.10,0:14:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 請等一下 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.70,0:14:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.80,0:14:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.90,0:14:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經生銹了呢 這個手銬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.80,0:14:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒帶手銬就帶上這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.00,0:14:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我爸爸的遺物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.20,0:14:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的手銬不是在東田先生的那次事件中弄壞了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.60,0:14:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我暫時就先用這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.30,0:15:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在正好給你當護身符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.10,0:15:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,護身符 妳父親不是因公殉職了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.00,0:15:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 那麼小心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.70,0:15:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤  （高木）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.70,0:15:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.20,0:15:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.10,0:15:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 去逮捕縱火犯還需要攜帶手槍嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.70,0:15:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 差遣高木警官他們的是刑事案偵察科
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.20,0:15:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與縱火犯有什麼關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.00,0:15:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為發現被刺殺的屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.60,0:15:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在第四件縱火案現場附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.10,0:15:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然無確鑿證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.50,0:15:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過可能死者因為目擊歹徒縱火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.40,0:15:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是要加以制止才遭到殺害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.60,0:15:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們出動就是因為這個原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.40,0:15:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你們千萬別離開我身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.40,0:15:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.10,0:16:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,品川站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.40,0:16:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警部 我是白鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.00,0:16:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經到了品川車站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.10,0:16:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把逃跑中的嫌疑犯逮捕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.90,0:16:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.00,0:16:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可當事人並不承認他是縱火犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.90,0:16:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是一個闖空門的小偷而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.60,0:16:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了 原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.30,0:16:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謎底揭曉了 我今天果然運氣奇佳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.10,0:16:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 佐藤警官的電話是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.70,0:16:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.90,0:16:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.70,0:16:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.20,0:16:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木 你要給誰打電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.90,0:16:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有 我去趟洗手間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.20,0:16:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.10,0:17:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我轉這個假面超人玩具機的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.40,0:17:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忽然有一個奇怪的叔叔從那裡出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.00,0:17:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是佐藤 啊 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.70,0:17:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼新進展嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.80,0:17:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你知道十八年前的兇手是誰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.80,0:17:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 根據我的推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.60,0:17:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聽了可不要嚇一跳哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.60,0:17:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人可能是我們今天上午見過的那四個人當中的某個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.70,0:17:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.80,0:17:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.10,0:17:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊 白鳥警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.90,0:17:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木 今天你的行動很可疑哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.80,0:17:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒呢 完全沒有的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.40,0:18:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我全明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.20,0:18:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愁思郎的真正涵義“カンオ”之謎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.20,0:18:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你的父親能鎖定犯人的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.20,0:18:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,徹頭徹尾地明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.30,0:18:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過時效畢竟已過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.80,0:18:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢…犯人究竟是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.40,0:18:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.00,0:18:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 高木 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.60,0:18:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.10,0:18:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木 高木 你怎麼了 快回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.60,0:19:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木 快回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.70,0:19:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木 高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.80,0:19:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.20,0:19:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.00,0:19:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻煩你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.60,0:19:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是白鳥 啊 佐藤警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.80,0:19:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛好把疑犯送到品川警局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.50,0:19:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃 高木嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.60,0:19:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有啊 值勤時還在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.50,0:19:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你快把最後看到他的時間和地點告訴總廳指揮部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.80,0:19:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木被人偷襲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.00,0:19:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在剛才跟我通話時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.10,0:19:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方很有可能是那個縱火犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.40,0:19:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要小心哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.60,0:19:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是高木警官是在電話裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.30,0:19:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要說出十八年前的犯人的時候被偷襲的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.30,0:19:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是不是表示…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.20,0:20:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.90,0:20:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個事件三年前就過時效了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.80,0:20:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且不知道他說的是不是正確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.80,0:20:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在傍晚遇到的那四個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.70,0:20:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說要去居酒屋喝酒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.20,0:20:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地點在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.70,0:20:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.60,0:20:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家店叫做七曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.10,0:20:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地點在品川車站前面的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.30,0:20:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果像剛才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.50,0:20:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高木警官在電話裡所說的犯人就在那四個人當中的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.60,0:20:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人可能和高木警官同在車站前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.60,0:20:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶然聽到了高木警官的談話內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.30,0:20:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是攻擊高木警官 企圖滅口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.40,0:20:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是很有可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.20,0:20:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總…總之 我去下品川車站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.40,0:20:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家先搭電車回家 明天到總廳去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.60,0:20:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.40,0:21:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊高木刑警的人也可能是縱火犯不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.90,0:21:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳不是應該帶上唯一的目擊證人步美去才對嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.30,0:21:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.30,0:21:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會加油的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.70,0:21:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.30,0:21:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫忙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.90,0:21:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.70,0:21:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警視廳呼叫各分局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.30,0:21:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及品川境內的調查人員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.80,0:21:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,案發地點在品川車站附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.00,0:21:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詳細情況仍不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.60,0:21:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過若發現一名員警被人毆打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.80,0:21:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.20,0:21:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請立刻通知本廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.20,0:21:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再重複一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.20,0:21:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警視廳呼叫各分局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.80,0:21:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及品川境內的調查人員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.50,0:21:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,案發地點在品川車站附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.20,0:21:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假的 這不是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.30,0:21:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那四個人當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.20,0:22:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺死我爸爸的兇手居然在那四個人當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.40,0:22:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.60,0:23:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人 那個人就是我看到的壞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.90,0:23:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不見了 那幾個孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.00,0:23:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣看得到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.90,0:24:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 難道說 襲擊高木的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.70,0:24:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.70,0:24:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 我們倆一起喝一杯慶祝慶祝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.80,0:24:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,カンオ先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.90,0:24:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.30,0:24:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本廳刑事的戀愛故事3 (後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.80,0:24:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN'S HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.50,0:24:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅馬字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.40,0:24:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回是解決篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.70,0:24:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是高木 精神飽滿中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.90,0:24:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.10,0:24:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了…哦哦
